data.description: Great opportunity to own this spacious 5 bedroom, 4 1/2 bath home in desirable  'The Oaks' neighborhood of Cane Bay Plantation! Convenience of Cane Bay schools, multiple work commute routes & access to the hot spots of Greater Charleston, along with the many community amenities offered - like the neighborhood pool, restaurants, shops, miles of walking/jogging trails, ... plus the YMCA!  This home boasts dual-master bedrooms (1 downstairs/1 upstairs), a huge loft, 2-car garage, screened-in back porch, back yard privacy fence, plenty of upgrades, ... PLUS it's in an 'X' Flood Zone!  The entire interior of the home has been Freshly Painted! *Seller is Offering a $4000 CARPET ALLOWANCE w/Acceptable Offer!! What an excellent family home to call your own!!!
